{"tid":1405410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"18區連儂放映會- 8月6日北角站","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:17:52.000Z","uid":114654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f0c1d9d340eaf5a3993dbb61a9f6b7626f9118","tid":1405410,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"7月30日喺西灣河，幾班人搞事我地唔驚<br />\n8月1日喺柴灣，橫風橫雨我地唔驚<br />\n今次喺北角，好紅好多鄉親會我地都唔會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期: 8月6日 星期四 <br />\n時間: 7:30 pm - 10:00pm<br />\n地點: 北角 (會有多於一個播放點)<br />\n<br />\n有經驗兼齊播放裝備? <br />\n- 當日7:30pm 開始，喺北角自己選擇適合既地方放影<br />\n*記得喺TG Group 分享你既位置，一黎兄弟可以幫手睇住，二黎啲位冇咁易撞<br />\n<br />\n冇裝備但想現埸 Support?<br />\n- 有額外一套完整放映器材(想借用可以PM Admin)<br />\n- 保住兄弟安全<br />\n北角算係半大佬(終極大佬係元朗)，保障兄弟安全最緊要，大家可以去唔同播放點支持，同睇住放映者安全，一有咩事立即喺TG Group道講，咁大家可以即刻去幫手<br />\n- 現埸派發傳單<br />\n- 現埸佈置連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n想支持但未必去到現埸?<br />\n善長可以捐助<br />\n<br />\n- 放映器材: 投影機/ 發電機/流動電箱/投影幕<br />\n(方法: 喺TG Group 內聯絡admin)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請即加入tg group 傾下一齊幫手: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M6S0jxXGk9BqvgjaZ3z1HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM6S0jxXGk9BqvgjaZ3z1HA&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=92ec0a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/M6S0jxXGk9BqvgjaZ3z1HA</a>"},{"pid":"90b4cbf07432a531ea2ae74e78bf42acb510bb3e","tid":1405410,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a174430ddd664bc061fbfbc5e579365724d9e190","tid":1405410,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:23:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4de1b75eaecd264d64ba4e566c21483f3f5c4c9","tid":1405410,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c42b66